label.phrase: when our a amp r guy lost his job we knew it was time for a change a few years ago that might've been a scary thing but it's a brand-new world out there now for bands like us we no longer have to rely on a big record company to make things happen and that's exciting we made this record without the pressure of having to write four smash hit singles hanging over our heads and that was liberating of course
